title: Wall Street Breakfast December 27: Jingle All The Way?
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Wednesday marked the biggest post-Christmas rally for U.S. stocks ever, a U.S. trade team will travel to Beijing to hold talks with Chinese officials, and India will ban e-commerce companies from selling products in which they have an equity interest.
